# enclave-sign-api standards

- Supabase edge handlers orchestrate; cryptography comes from vendored `@enclave/sign-sdk`.
- Never duplicate crypto inline or import `@noble/*` in handler code.
- `supabase/functions/_vendor/` is generated — run `npm run vendor` before deploy.
- Handler helpers live in `supabase/functions/_shared/sign/`.
- Build sibling `enclave-pqc-primitives` and `enclave-sign-sdk` before `npm run vendor`.
